00:08:27.480 --> 00:08:31.380
And now there's a syntax for positional-only arguments, right?

00:08:31.380 --> 00:08:32.440
You don't need to know.

00:08:32.440 --> 00:08:32.840
It's cool.

00:08:32.840 --> 00:08:33.240
Yeah.

